- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image retrieval and visual search engines. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with wearable cameras and personal objects. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper proposes a retrieval pipeline and evaluation scheme. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the application of the proposed system is to help users find their personal belongings. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve some machine learning techniques for object recognition and retrieval.
